{
  "stem": "131.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They put on her lice, living lice, and how much they can produce [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to-- to suck her blood.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was sitting with each hair, taking between my two fingers, and pulling down the dead-- the dead lice.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was so stupid to ask her, how on earth did you let yourself-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that you didn't care?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then she explained that how she got that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, all those things I never knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never heard from nobody that what they did [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with other people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like with my cousin, who was liberated from Eng-- English soldiers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put him in cold barrel and in hot barrel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he got colitis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He almost died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They cut here out pieces for him, constantly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was very sick after that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You hear those stories what people went through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You can't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stole food from those people and tried to feed her, spoon by spoon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't want to stay in her stomach.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A long time, nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] then [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it came, the Red Cross, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and ask, who is from Czechoslovakia?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they took us home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hannah and me went back to Czechoslovakia, to Prague.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I met there an engineer who was working with my father.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 13 SECONDS] I was living [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with Hannah there in Prague.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they said that they're looking for us here, because they didn't want the Czech people that we should come back from the Sudeten, because that didn't belong to them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't want-- but anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I thought for the American people when I got liberated.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
